        public TodoItem​(java.lang.Integer id,
                java.lang.String text,
                java.lang.Boolean completed,
                java.util.Date due,
                java.lang.Integer priority,
                java.lang.String category)
        Constructor for TodoItem
        Parameters:
        id - - id of the item, will be generated by TodoModel
        text - - a description of the task to be done
        completed - - indicates whether the task is completed or incomplete, will be false by default
        due - - a due date
        priority - - an integer indicating the priority of the todo, must be between 1 and 3, will be 3 by default
        category - - a user-specified String that can be used to group related todos
